data.description: Inviting and well-designed, this home features three spacious bedrooms and two full bathrooms! The open floorplan seamlessly connects the living spaces, accentuating the real hardwood floors that add a touch of warmth and sophistication. Abundant natural light bathes the interior, creating an airy and welcoming ambiance. Additionally, the property includes a one-car carport and an extended driveway for convenient parking. Enjoy an oversized backyard with a new fence, providing both privacy and a secure space for outdoor activities for you and/or your furry friends! Completing the picture, a shed offers additional storage, enhancing the functionality of this delightful home.
